    public static final class DetailedValidationError.ErrorType
extends com.vmware.vapi.bindings.ApiEnumeration<DetailedValidationError.ErrorType>
    The ErrorType enum contains the possible types of errors related to property validation. This enumeration was added in vSphere API 8.0.2.0.

    See enumerated types description.
